snippet.title: Dead Cells: The Bad Seed - Official Animated Trailer
snippet.description:
Behold Dead Cells' furious, headless protagonist in all its animated glory in this The Bad Seed DLC launch trailer ahead of the February 11 release date on Xbox One, PS4, PC, and Nintendo Switch.

Explore a relaxing Arboretum, wade through a noxious Swamp and take on a new boss in this new early game content designed to expand the Dead Cells universe and add variety to runs for people who want to support the development of the game. For more information, visit the Dead Cells The Bad Seed page on the Steam store.
